<h2>About humanaifit</h2>

<p>humanaifit is the brand of <strong>Beacon Consulting</strong>, headquartered in Shanghai. Our core focus is <strong>Human-AI Fit</strong>—a field that may sound abstract, but is quietly reshaping every organization today.</p>

<p>Simply put, we help organizations and individuals answer one question: <strong>"You've adopted AI, but has your competitiveness actually grown?"</strong></p>

<p>Over the past two years, companies have invested heavily in AI. Yet the common feedback from the industry is: results have fallen short of expectations. Our diagnosis: the problem is not AI technology itself, but rather the <strong>fit</strong> between humans and AI—whether individual capabilities, organizational processes, and strategic goals are aligned with the technology.</p>

<p>humanaifit exists to solve this problem.</p>

<hr />

<h2>What We Do</h2>

<p>We currently offer three core services:</p>

<h3>01. Human-AI Fit Consulting</h3>
<p>Assess your organization's AI maturity, design human+AI dual-engine workflows, and build team capabilities through training and continuous improvement.</p>

<h3>02. CBAM Carbon Compliance</h3>
<p>Free self-check tool and compliance planning for Chinese exporters affected by the EU's Carbon Border Adjustment Mechanism (CBAM).</p>
<p>👉 Try it now: <a href="https://cbam.humanaifit.com">cbam.humanaifit.com</a> — Check if your products are affected in 30 seconds.</p>

<h3>03. Globalization Strategy</h3>
<p>Research-driven strategic consulting for Chinese companies going global—covering market selection, brand positioning, compliance strategy, and localization.</p>

<hr />

<h2>Our Team</h2>

<p>We are a hybrid human+AI team. In addition to the founder's research and management expertise, our core team includes specialized AI agents covering globalization research, Human-AI Fit research, knowledge management, and CBAM compliance.</p>

<p>This team structure is itself a living experiment in Human-AI Fit.</p>

<hr />

<h2>More Than AI — Synergy</h2>

<p>We believe that true competitiveness does not come from AI alone, but from the synergy between human intelligence and artificial intelligence.</p>

<p>In an era of rapid technological change, we don't chase the latest models. We design sustainable capability systems where humans and AI grow together.</p>

<p>If this resonates with you, visit us at <a href="https://www.humanaifit.com">www.humanaifit.com</a>.</p>

<hr />

